Pflugerville.Wells Branch, Texas:
Wells Branch is a census-designated place (CDP) in Travis County, Texas, United States. The population was 12,120 at the 2010 census.


== Geography ==
Wells Branch is located at 30°26′38″N 97°40′42″W (30.443997, -97.678469), 13 miles (21 km) north of downtown Austin.
